                  Rubadue Wire Co., Inc. is a producer of "articles" and
                  therefore must rely on suppliers for pre-registration. When a
                  new list of SVHC is released, Rubadue Wire Co., Inc. takes due
                  diligence with its supply chain to determine compliance.
